data.name: MANUAL RETRACTABLE SAFETY SYRINGES
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Barrel + Plunger: Medical Grade Polypropylene (PP)
- Gasket: Isoprene Latex-Free Rubber

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Luer Lock Tip
- Fixed, Mounted Needle and Without Needle
- Latex-free Gasket
- Customizable graduation including logo

## PERFORMANCE
- Easy Activation Safety Mechanism
- inviolable closure technology
- Clear graduation printing technology
- High Transparency Barrel
- Smooth sliding
- Smooth Surface
- CLICK AND SET
- INJECTION
- EXTRA SAFE
- DIAGNOSTIC
